      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but it's just... seeing them struggle to help me, it feels selfish to keep making them do it. i've spent my whole life looking after people and now it feels like i'm just a heavy weight they're forced to carry. sometimes i think the kindest thing i could do for them is just... not be a burden anymore. it feels almost more selfless to just let go.",
