    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... i think they would be better off. i see the look on their faces when they have to help me. it's like they're just doing it out of duty, not love. wouldn't they be more free if they didn't have to worry about me all the time? if i just... quietly exited, they could finally have their lives back without this constant shadow over them. it's like i'm holding them back from everything.",
